OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FLeicester City's relegation from the
OL,8,FChampionship is remarkable.
OL,10,FIt comes only ten years after the club
OL,11,Fwon the Premier League and six years
OL,12,Fafter they won the FA Cup.
OL,14,FThey are the second only team to have
OL,15,Fboth won the Premier League and be
OL,16,Frelegated to the third tier alongside
OL,17,FBlackburn Rovers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FThey also join another unhappy club
OL,8,Fwith Blackburn Rovers and Leeds United
OL,9,Fas the only teams to have played in
OL,10,Fboth the Champions League and League
OL,11,FOne.
OL,13,FThe Foxes also have one of the most
OL,14,Fexpensive squads in the Championship
OL,15,Fwith an estimated market value of more
OL,16,Fthan #140 million.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FThat makes their squad worth more than
OL,8,FCharlton Athletic, Portsmouth, Oxford
OL,9,FUnited, and Blackburn Rovers combined,
OL,10,Fwith all four of those teams sitting
OL,11,Fabove them in the table.
OL,13,FThis follows a run of only one win in
OL,14,Ftheir last 16 games. They have now
OL,15,Fsuffered back-to-back relegations,
OL,16,Fhaving finished 18th in the Premier
OL,17,FLeague last season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FThe Foxes may have a fighting chance
OL,8,Fof staying in the division if it
OL,9,Fweren't for a six-point deduction they
OL,10,Fwere given by the Premier League.
OL,12,FBut, even without the points
OL,13,Fdeduction, the club would still be in
OL,14,Fthe relegation zone.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FThe penalty came after the club was
OL,8,Ffound in breach of financial rules by
OL,9,Fthe Independent Disciplinary
OL,10,FCommission, appointed under Premier
OL,11,FLeague Rules, for having breached the
OL,12,FProfit and Sustainability Rules by
OL,13,Fmore than 20 million pounds over a
OL,14,Fthree-year reporting period ending
OL,15,Fwith the 2023/24 season.
OL,17,FBoth parties have submitted their
OL,18,Fappeals to the Chair of the Judicial
OL,19,FPanel. An Appeal Board will then be
OL,20,Fappointed to hear the case.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
