OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,FFrom Premier League champions to
OL,8,Frelegation from the Championship,
OL,9,Fhere's a timeline of Leicester's
OL,10,Frollercoaster decade:
OL,12,F2015-16: Leicester were crowned
OL,13,FPremier League champions under Claudio
OL,14,FRanieri. They finished 10 points ahead
OL,15,Fof second-placed Arsenal to guarantee
OL,16,Ftheir spot in the Champions League for
OL,17,Fthe first time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2016-17: Leicester sacked Ranieri in
OL,8,FFebruary 2017, made it to the quarter-
OL,9,Ffinals of the Champions League and
OL,10,Ffinished 14th in the English top
OL,11,Fflight.
OL,13,F2017-18: Following a run of just one
OL,14,Fwin from their opening eight matches,
OL,15,Fnew boss Craig Shakespeare departed,
OL,16,Fand Claude Puel was put in charge.
OL,17,FThey achieved a ninth-placed finish.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
