PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2018-19: Leicester were 12th when they
OL,8,Fsacked Puel, but Brendan Rodgers'
OL,9,Fappointment helped them finish ninth.
OL,10,FThis season would be remembered more
OL,11,Ffor what happened off the pitch, after
OL,12,Fa helicopter crash killed Foxes owner
OL,13,FVichai Srivaddhanaprabha and four
OL,14,Fothers on October 27.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2019-20: Leicester City had their best
OL,8,Fseason since winning the league as
OL,9,Fthey finished fifth and went on an 11-
OL,10,Fgame unbeaten run in all competitions.
OL,11,FAlong the way, they beat Southampton 9-
OL,12,F0, which still stands as the joint
OL,13,Fbiggest win in Premier League history.
OL,15,F2020-21: Leicester hit new highs and
OL,16,Flifted the FA Cup for the first time
OL,17,Fwith a 1-0 victory over Chelsea. But
OL,18,Fit could have been a season of much
OL,19,Fmore for the club, whose Europa League
OL,20,Fjourney ended in the last-16 phase,
OL,21,Fand they missed out on the top-four.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2021-22: Leicester defeated Manchester
OL,8,FCity to win the Community Shield and
OL,9,Freached a first-ever continental semi-
OL,10,Ffinal in the Conference League. They
OL,11,Fwere knocked out by Jose Mourinho's
OL,12,Feventual winners, Roma.
OL,14,F2022-23: The Foxes were relegated from
OL,15,Fthe top flight after a run of five
OL,16,Fdefeats in six games. Brendan Rodgers
OL,17,Fwas sacked, and new boss Dean Smith
OL,18,Fcouldn't save them from the
OL,19,FChampionship.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2023-24: Leicester went straight back
OL,8,Fto the Premier League by winning the
OL,9,FChampionship for a record eighth time.
OL,10,FAfter leading the team to an
OL,11,Fimpressive title win, manager Enzo
OL,12,FMaresca was poached by Chelsea.
OL,14,F2024-25: New man Steve Cooper couldn't
OL,15,Freplicate Maresca's success and was
OL,16,Fsacked after just 12 games. He was
OL,17,Freplaced by Ruud van Nistelrooy. But
OL,18,Fthe Foxes suffered 15 defeats from 16
OL,19,Fleague games and were relegated in
OL,20,F18th place.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776834276
OL,3,CPremier League champions to League
OL,4,COne: Why Leicester's relegation is
OL,5,Cremarkable
OL,7,F2025-26: Leicester had an encouraging
OL,8,Fstart under Marti Cifuentes, but
OL,9,Fthings soon unravelled, and the
OL,10,Fmanager departed in January to be
OL,11,Freplaced by Gary Rowett. The following
OL,12,Fmonth, they were deducted six points
OL,13,Fbefore a run of one win from 18
OL,14,Fmatches left them on the verge of
OL,15,FLeague One, just 10 years after
OL,16,Fwinning the Premier League.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
